name: Swole Apes #2982
description: 8,888 Swole Apes have lifted themselves up and risen to fend off the oncoming goblin hordes. The Bored Ape masses have proven themselves physically incapable. These elite apes, however, have proven and forged themselves, both physically and mentally, amongst the trials and tribulations of the iron temple. Thus, the Swole Ape Fitness Club was conceived.
